description:
Is heaven just a boring place with harps and puffy white clouds? Or, is it a place where we have all the attractions of this world? What is heaven really like? If we look to the Source of Heaven Himself, God reveals through His Word that heaven is beyond anything we have ever imagined. 

Join Pastor Ted Wilson as he unlocks the mysteries of Heaven through the book of Revelation! Discover how you can get ready now to be a citizen of that long-desired Paradise!  

Pastor Wilson is sharing Revelation of Hope directly from Indianapolis, IN.
